<dl id="sa0511bz"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="sa" href="#sa0511bz">SA (VI.A) </a>: <a href="../../FF/fnbs/ssaall.htm#sa0511bz"> 511(bz)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> bowed the chin of doubt on collar of reflection,</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[A certain religious leader, on being asked what he might do on finding himself in a beautiful garden with a handsome young man, and assured privacy]</font> <mark>bowed the chin of doubt upon the collar of meditation</mark>; and, too honest to lie, presently whispered, &ldquo;Allah defend me from such temptation of Satan!&rdquo; <small> Richard Burton, &ldquo;Terminal Essay&rdquo; in <a name="RB01" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#RB01"><cite title="source">1000 Nights and 1 Night</cite></a> (Denver, 1919) x.234</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
